## 9. Maintenance
- Refresh nodes/topology: `/discover-agents`.
- Reconcile permission drift: re-run `/discover-agents` (it rewrites the topology from
  the live `agent_permissions`), compare against the intent in §5, then re-run
  `/compose-system` to push §5 back into the manifest.
- Regenerate the manifest from §5 intent: `/compose-system`.
- Bring deployed agents to their GitHub HEAD (non-destructive, pull-only): `/sync-fleet-to-head`.
- Re-interview agents & correct this narrative against reality: `/profile-fleet`.
- Fold already-verified deltas (fixes applied, audit corrections) into this narrative
  and the other doc surfaces without new interviews: `/fleet-reconcile`.
